{"type": "article", "id": 21473, "title": "纸水瓶", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-29T07:34:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104604o5jhC6Ptw7xWKVAN.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t美国设计师 Luigi Rausch 发明了一种纸水瓶，试图替代不环保的塑料瓶。与普通纸杯不同的是，他在纸瓶中间加了一层波浪芯纸，增强了厚度，也避免压坏。而为了真正达到环保的目的，他使用蜂蜡来替代纸杯所使用的 PE 淋膜，在帮助防水的同时，也可以帮助分解。产品目前还是一个概念，<a href=\"http://www.behance.net/gallery/26654151/Paper-Water-Co\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726151002xEFOBe0nPip2CkYv.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"763\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072615100340X6PrKh9izNlwWH.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"763\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726151003COuUjQ5B23sKvqXy.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"763\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072615100446gUei8vIXn3Vo1z.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"763\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}